{"tid":1667360,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史從來得兩種起義係成功","createTime":"2019-10-21T12:01:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T16:27:04.000Z","uid":92836,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e1e32f8890eb7ea8c66c01a78982b76770101716","tid":1667360,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:01:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>武裝起義or宗教起義</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nThat&rsquo;s why 淋病本會極速落去清真寺做show<br />\n<br />\n因為南亞宗教力量係一股大力量扎根全球<br />\n不論軟實力定硬實力<br />\n<br />\n我地要更加同佢哋 Connect 起來<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n覺得有道理可以傾下"},{"pid":"b6eda541296ca4709f8b794490dc0984838b551e","tid":1667360,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:09:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"085baac269d28b9f3dbf251de2c322387dd6c23a","tid":1667360,"uid":132056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:11:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天滅中共 全黨死清光</span></span>"},{"pid":"bdd72461e2dbd53b6c792218fc7d0988a0b3bcea","tid":1667360,"uid":271947,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:24:36.000Z","msg":"唔係想潑冷水，連新疆集中營都connect唔到全世界穆斯林反抗，香港一間清真寺污糟咗又如何"},{"pid":"91e9162c1dfa24a7001cac8ab8fe50d4c17a2016","tid":1667360,"uid":169195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bdd72461e2dbd53b6c792218fc7d0988a0b3bcea","tid":1667360,"uid":271947,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:24:36.000Z","msg":"唔係想潑冷水，連新疆集中營都connect唔到全世界穆斯林反抗，香港一間清真寺污糟咗又如何"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:29:29.000Z","msg":"Sad but true"},{"pid":"8457e3409b9045041cbbf58573387a5bf1c4cbf1","tid":1667360,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:29:54.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"7579489a4d58f915f4e872adc6433067a3a69053","tid":1667360,"uid":130770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0775b97c04aa7213da43846d0c921ddd4c1035","tid":1667360,"uid":31545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:36:23.000Z","msg":"Free Uyghurs"},{"pid":"83aae2d4df289e2c60df86e1c40222d1f8279671","tid":1667360,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:08:06.000Z","msg":"唔止謝sir，連er er er sir都&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d4691f92e273ed878238bda7d2153d6e3bb77a6e","tid":1667360,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:08:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ba549d0e90b54a7844b713ceeb2cde712522bdfd","tid":1667360,"uid":174174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:29:18.000Z","msg":"有冇南亞俾共產黨壓迫嘅資料<br />\n可以拎去做文宣"},{"pid":"91da1bcf034a1f983e23066b17563fc051faedac","tid":1667360,"uid":289768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba549d0e90b54a7844b713ceeb2cde712522bdfd","tid":1667360,"uid":174174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:29:18.000Z","msg":"有冇南亞俾共產黨壓迫嘅資料<br />\n可以拎去做文宣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:42:33.000Z","msg":"